      "display_name": "Seeed Studio XIAO ESP32-S3 (Pre-Soldered SKU) \u2014 coin-sized 21 \u00d7 17",
      "name": "esp32-s3-xiao",
      "version": "0.2.0",
      "description": "Seeed Studio XIAO ESP32-S3 (Pre-Soldered SKU) \u2014 coin-sized 21 \u00d7 17.5 mm ESP32-S3 board around the ESP32-S3R8 die (Xtensa LX7 dual-core, 8 MB flash + 8 MB octal PSRAM). USB-C with native USB-Serial-JTAG. On-board LiPo charger + buck regulator with BAT+/BAT\u2212 solder pads on the back (no JST-PH). Only 11 broken-out GPIOs (D0\u2013D10). FSM status LED is the on-board mono yellow LED on GPIO21 (LEDC PWM driven) \u2014 same mono-LED pattern as the dfr1117 carrier, no external WS2812 required. r2-workshop's alternative Xtensa carrier (ADR-001 promoted it briefly, ADR-002 reverted default to DevKitC); fully supported.",
