          "class": "ai.reality2.workshop.sensor.identity",
          "description": "One-shot at boot. Loads or creates the device's persistent Ed25519 keypair + the persistent RBID (R2-FNV(device_pk)) from NVS, sets them in the hive context, then enters idle. Mirrors the R2-HIVE device-identity contract \u2014 every subsequent sentant (Bootstrap, Beacon, Uplink, \u2026) consumes the keypair from the hive context. Compilable subset (R2-COMPILE \u00a73.1).",
